• Approach
  • About us
Dataskai is developed by a team of programmers and ML-enthusiasts
the framework for AI/ML projects concentrated on team work and rapid development

Hide target for test set. Without exceptions

We want to spread the best practices of teamwork and programming in teams developing ML/AI projects.

We think that existing products do not offer the proper tradeoff between speed and reliability of the resulting ML/AI solution.

Tools for team workflow

  • Team Leaderboard
  • Project Wizard
  • Data Loader and Data Store
  • Feature Loader and Feature Store
  • Metrics Service and Submits Storage
  • Feature Extractor and Prediction Builder
Team Leaderboard
This interface allows you to&nbsp;check metrics for all submitted solutions on&nbsp;current task, search for best/worst metric values, make fast text search for submits, hide some fields, etc. Moreover, breadcrumbs on&nbsp;top of&nbsp;the window allows you to&nbsp;switch to&nbsp;all available in&nbsp;GUI tasks and check out scores on&nbsp;it.

Make frequent operations easier

even don't do it at all

  • Templates
    Wizard for generating and configuring ML/AI projects. Project structure and architecture fitted for long running projects (1month +).
  • Architecture
    EService-oriented architecture, based on docker technology. Framework is built on top of opensource products, libraries and components.
  • Installation
    Use local installation on your own premises for short-term team work, or installation in datacenters/cloud premises for corporate use.
  • MLOps
    Deploy AI/ML solutions in framework instance. Datascientist have end-to-end responsibility for the whole AI/ML solution.
